Title: SPATIAL REPRESENTATIONS OF METEOROLOGICAL DATA FOR INTELLIGENT RETRIEVAL  
Author: Eric K. Jones and Aaron Roydhouse 
Date: May 17th-19th 1994.  
Note: Presented at the Sixth Colloquium of the Spatial  1.0 INTRODUCTION  
